                <h1>Junot Díaz provides valuable insights for creative writers in the Duke community </h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/889c220b-f148-4e97-bd63-7d17931eba02.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Junot&#x20;D&#x00ED;az&#x20;came&#x20;to&#x20;Duke&#x27;s&#x20;campus&#x20;on&#x20;Monday&#x20;night&#x20;for&#x20;a&#x20;reading&#x20;and&#x20;Q&amp;A.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Junot Díaz came to Duke's campus on Monday night for a reading and Q&A.&nbsp;</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
